		font-weight: 700;
		margin:0;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
		margin-top:1rem;
	}
	.box .apply h4 {
		font-size:1.14rem;
		color:#9e9e9e;
		margin:0;
		margin-bottom: .4rem;
	}
